The entities package handles the sentient beings which occupy the game world.

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    InventoryListener
    The InventoryListener is used to listen for changes to a Player's inventory, firing whenever they pick up or lost an AbstractItem.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description

    The AbstractEntity is a basic implementation of MobileWorldObject.
    Player
    A Player is an AbstractEntity which can pick up and use AbstractItems.

Package gears.sidescroller.world.entities Description

The entities package handles the sentient beings which occupy the game world. Future versions will add AI-controlled denizens for the world, and the serialization they will require.
